        "COMPLETION: reserve : [#void#]reserve({#<#size_type __res_arg#>#})
        "COMPLETION: GameClean (Hidden) : [#void#]MB_GAME::GameClean()
        "=======================================================================
        if sLine[:11] ==# 'COMPLETION: '
